<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Domain Monitoring System</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <header>
            <div class="header-content">
                <div>
                    <h1>üåê Domain Monitoring System</h1>
                    <p>Track domain availability for your keywords</p>
                </div>
                <button class="btn btn-secondary" id="open-logs-btn">üìú System Logs</button>
                <button class="btn btn-secondary" id="settings-btn">‚öôÔ∏è Settings</button>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- (Rest of body...) -->

        <!-- Logs Modal -->
        <div id="logs-modal" class="modal">
            <div class="modal-content modal-lg">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h2>üìú System Logs</h2>
                    <span class="close" id="close-logs">&times;</span>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <div class="logs-container">
                        <textarea id="system-logs" readonly placeholder="Waiting for logs..."></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="log-actions">
                        <button class="btn btn-secondary" id="refresh-logs-btn">üîÑ Refresh Logs</button>
                        <button class="btn btn-danger" id="clear-logs-btn">üóëÔ∏è Clear Logs</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- System Status -->
        <div class="status-card">
            <div class="status-item">
                <span class="status-label">Keywords Monitored:</span>
                <span class="status-value" id="keywords-count">0</span>
            </div>
            <div class="status-item">
                <span class="status-label">Domains Found:</span>
                <span class="status-value" id="domains-count">0</span>
            </div>
            <div class="status-item">
                <span class="status-label">Email Alerts:</span>
                <span class="status-value" id="email-status" style="font-size: 0.9em; cursor: pointer;"
                    onclick="document.getElementById('open-settings-btn').click()">‚ö†Ô∏è Enter Email to Get Alerts</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Content Grid -->
        <div class="content-grid">
            <!-- Add Keywords Section -->
            <div class="card">
                <h2>‚ûï Add Keywords</h2>
                <form id="keyword-form">
                    <textarea id="keywords-input"
                        placeholder="Enter keywords (one per line or comma-separated)&#10;Example:&#10;tech startup&#10;ai tools&#10;cloud hosting"
                        rows="5"></textarea>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Add Keywords</button>
                </form>
            </div>

            <!-- Upload CSV Section -->
            <div class="card">
                <h2>üìÅ Upload CSV</h2>
                <div class="upload-area" id="upload-area">
                    <input type="file" id="csv-file" accept=".csv" hidden>
                    <div class="upload-prompt">
                        <svg width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor"
                            stroke-width="2">
                            <path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"></path>
                            <polyline points="17 8 12 3 7 8"></polyline>
                            <line x1="12" y1="3" x2="12" y2="15"></line>
                        </svg>
                        <p>Click to upload or drag and drop</p>
                        <span class="file-info">CSV file with keywords (one per line)</span>
                    </div>
                    <button class="btn btn-secondary" id="upload-btn">Select CSV File</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Results Section -->
        <div class="card results-card">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h2>üéØ Available Domains</h2>
                <div class="actions">
                    <button class="btn btn-danger" id="clear-btn">üóëÔ∏è Clear Data</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-primary" id="scan-now-btn">‚ö° Scan Now</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-secondary" id="refresh-btn">üîÑ Refresh</button>
                    <button class="btn btn-success" id="download-btn">üì• Download CSV</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="loading" class="loading" style="display: none;">
                <div class="spinner"></div>
                <p>Loading results...</p>
            </div>

            <div id="no-results" class="no-results" style="display: none;">
                <svg width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                    <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                    <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"></line>
                    <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"></line>
                </svg>
                <p>No available domains found yet</p>
                <span>Add keywords and wait for the monitoring service to run</span>
            </div>

            <div class="table-wrapper" id="results-table-wrapper" style="display: none;">
                <table id="results-table">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>Domain</th>
                            <th>Keyword</th>
                            <th>Checked Date</th>
                            <th>Email Sent</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody id="results-body">
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Toast Notification -->
        <div id="toast" class="toast"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Settings Modal -->
    <div id="settings-modal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h2>‚öôÔ∏è Email Configuration</h2>
                <span class="close" id="close-settings">&times;</span>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <form id="settings-form">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="smtp-server">SMTP Server</label>
                        <input type="text" id="smtp-server" placeholder="smtp.gmail.com" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="smtp-port">SMTP Port</label>
                        <input type="number" id="smtp-port" placeholder="587" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="smtp-username">Email (Username)</label>
                        <input type="email" id="smtp-username" placeholder="your-email@gmail.com" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="smtp-password">App Password</label>
                        <input type="password" id="smtp-password" placeholder="App Password" required>
                        <small class="help-text">For Gmail, use an App Password, not your login password.</small>
                    </div>
                    <hr>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="smtp-from">From Email</label>
                        <input type="email" id="smtp-from" placeholder="same as username usually" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="smtp-to">To Email</label>
                        <input type="email" id="smtp-to" placeholder="where to receive alerts" required>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-actions">
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" id="test-email-btn">üìß Test Email</button>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">üíæ Save Settings</button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- System Logs Modal -->
    <div id="logs-modal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content modal-lg">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h2>üìú System Logs</h2>
                <span class="close" id="close-logs">&times;</span>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <div class="tabs">
                    <button class="tab-btn active" data-tab="logs-tab">üñ•Ô∏è System Logs</button>
                    <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="help-tab">‚ùì Help & Manual</button>
                </div>

                <!-- Logs Tab -->
                <div id="logs-tab" class="tab-content active">
                    <p class="logs-intro">View background activity and monitoring errors below.</p>
                    <div class="logs-container">
                        <textarea id="system-logs" readonly placeholder="Waiting for logs..."></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="log-actions">
                        <button class="btn btn-secondary" id="refresh-logs-btn">üîÑ Refresh Logs</button>
                        <button class="btn btn-danger" id="clear-logs-btn">üóëÔ∏è Clear Logs</button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Help Tab -->
                <div id="help-tab" class="tab-content">
                    <div class="help-section">
                        <h3>üìñ User Manual & Troubleshooting</h3>

                        <div class="manual-block">
                            <h4>1. Installation & Setup</h4>
                            <p>Once installed, the application runs in the background. It generates domains from your
                                keywords and checks their availability.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="manual-block">
                            <h4>2. Configure Email Alerts (Important!)</h4>
                            <p>To receive notifications, go to <strong>Settings</strong> and enter your SMTP details:
                            </p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><strong>Gmail:</strong> server: <code>smtp.gmail.com</code>, port: <code>587</code>
                                    (Use App Password)</li>
                                <li><strong>Outlook:</strong> server: <code>smtp.office365.com</code>, port:
                                    <code>587</code></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="manual-block">
                            <h4>3. Running Scans</h4>
                            <p>Click "Scan Now" to check domains immediately. The system also checks automatically every
                                30 minutes. Status "Available" means you can buy it!</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="manual-block">
                            <h4>4. Support</h4>
                            <p>Logs are available in the "System Logs" tab. If you find bugs, please check the logs and
                                contact support.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>

</html>